# ----------------- start docker security concerns ----------------- #
    # ----- Insecure credential storage:
        - Docker commandline provide login mechanism which allow to store the auth-token unencrypted at /root/.docker/config.json
    # ----- Docker default user
        - By default the docker run the commands with root privilege.
        - Using USER command to create new user and run commands with new user privilege instead of root.
# -----------------   end docker security concerns ----------------- #